{"tid":646180,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"濕疹真係好難頂⋯⋯","createTime":"2018-04-28T19:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T12:51:28.000Z","uid":76490,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3c12215033b550a3f90e0640b3dc2ab05419b5","tid":646180,"uid":76490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:28:48.000Z","msg":"我女朋友e排開始濕疹勁左，唔止手，仲連面都開始有，成日話好痕好痕，買左好多野比佢都無用仲係好痕，所以我就諗住同佢戒口，但濕疹好似乜都唔食得（豬，牛，雞，羊都唔得），所以想問下出街食同屋企食嘅話食咩最好？<br />\n<br />\n出街好似真係無選擇⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b02107cd00d5f5dfaca9cd91a9004534c626516","tid":646180,"uid":71008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:35:53.000Z","msg":"冇，去睇醫生，唔需要戒口"},{"pid":"20a583d41348e3dede0ab45a33bef3b18203edce","tid":646180,"uid":76490,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4b02107cd00d5f5dfaca9cd91a9004534c626516","tid":646180,"uid":71008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:35:53.000Z","msg":"冇，去睇醫生，唔需要戒口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:38:32.000Z","msg":"有睇中醫，但想同佢戒下口快啲好返咁姐"},{"pid":"f2c79c3ed3b8cf5d0bb850b2a7b0aed5f1d20c85","tid":646180,"uid":6179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:42:01.000Z","msg":"之前睇西醫 食完d藥勁暈勁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9d66de21ee5e755c6e89babe5f6c1bf29d21e4","tid":646180,"uid":148201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:45:55.000Z","msg":"塊面無啦啦紅左真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ee5d887087a67104c7e1eb56ee0aa6f1fcdddd","tid":646180,"uid":76490,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2c79c3ed3b8cf5d0bb850b2a7b0aed5f1d20c85","tid":646180,"uid":6179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:42:01.000Z","msg":"之前睇西醫 食完d藥勁暈勁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla